SELECT 
    title,
    inception,
    movement,
    genre,
    image_url,
    img_path,
    COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY image_url) as duplicate_count
FROM paintings
WHERE image_url IN (
    SELECT image_url
    FROM paintings
    GROUP BY image_url
    HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)
ORDER BY image_url, inception
